{"tid":1467864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於「不割席」，我咁睇","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:42:49.000Z","uid":86237,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"577519567f461d4a17a6c08f24208a64d788645c","tid":1467864,"uid":86237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"割席同反對並無衝突。做咩野都會有人認同和反對。有人話要理智啲，有人話要郁手，有人話唔應該衝，有人話要升級。唔同意見，唔代表割席。<br />\n<br />\n呢個運動不嬲都係organic 咁進行。無大台，無單一意見，你能夠香港人一齊二百萬人上街，衝立會後仍然攞到支持，唔係必然，係不斷宣揚、反駁、文宣捱返黎既結果，中間果陣我地自己內部都有好多做法上既爭執。<br />\n<br />\n不割席，係顯示我地團結，但唔係一個道德束縛。你認為係啱既野，你要講；你認為係錯既野，你都提出。唔係話因為我覺得唔應該咁做就唔做，點解先？提出囉，說服囉，包裝囉，拉攏支持自己既人囉，唔係嫁話咩叫兄弟爬山各自努力？如果有條友爬爬下行錯路跌左落山，你覺得唔割席係唔理佢繼續行上去呀？定諗辦法幫佢急救？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔指責得前線？前線狼起上黎真係可以好狼，唔平衡下在場有幾多人但都繼續叫人死守路口既人都有。怕有鬼？我都有碇磚，大把前線做一d後排唔會主動做或支持既野。做主流民意以外既野就預左卑人指責，呢個係社會正常現象，咁點算呀？點唔割席？幫佢補飛囉，解釋、文宣、拉攏。<br />\n<br />\n我唔割席唔代表我支持你，只係代表我會盡我方法黎保你。"},{"pid":"35861bcc744b6af311b2712cbc0b1d01363dc9f2","tid":1467864,"uid":38779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"好文要推<br />\n核彈都唔割<br />\n大家都要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0734caf77b8e62fde740a99fadb86d65966a4f67","tid":1467864,"uid":53941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4a10fabba268622a395cd754103735c04c48bd","tid":1467864,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"推呀 <br />\n有唔同睇法冇問題 攞出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a11761a4041accd08b369ebead8a52d05e1ffc","tid":1467864,"uid":53941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"要貼堂"},{"pid":"0afb188aa662cebd2719d7bb5882348a2a0d513d","tid":1467864,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾句建議姐818 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各自爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"1dd20c738c819ec86882058c412ede78e0957ea1","tid":1467864,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"分乜撚野化？？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467706</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29461d7aee7b0bcedda0c54c981c14c90e6506d5","tid":1467864,"uid":185000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:52.000Z","msg":"唔割！"},{"pid":"7aa68255e6c85db363644fdbef53678ff48ba686","tid":1467864,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"唔岩就要屌，屌完就補鑊"},{"pid":"0ed2489535f2d83e0746c5cf34786863d32072b5","tid":1467864,"uid":139007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"f5bd9aaa203269c2b19ab8ef78b44b26abe69f0d","tid":1467864,"uid":86237,"like":0,"dislik